data.description: Nestled into a gated getaway is Hidden Villa Dr., your next home sweet home! This is an extremely low maintenance, well built, garden style home awaiting its next chapter. It's located on the exterior perimeter of the neighborhood which provides a dose of extra privacy and seclusion. Great curb appeal that invites you right in to a freshly painted interior. You'll notice beautiful wood flooring through the living and dining which compliments all of the natural light pouring in. A cozy fireplace and tall ceilings give a grandiose feel. You've got a bedroom right off of the living room but would also be a great spot for an office, playroom, hobby room, etc. Your kitchen has all you need and more with granite counters, ample storage, gas cooktop, and stainless appliances. Right off of the kitchen is your laundry, additional bedroom, and additional bath. Down the hall you'll pass a built in desk area which then leads to your primary suite. Your primary is extremely spacious with a tray ceiling and lots of natural light. Your primary bath has dual sinks, a jetted tub, separate shower, and a large walk in closet. Upstairs is another bedroom with lots of space and a full bath. Out the backdoor is a cozy courtyard ideal for relaxing or entertaining guests. This neighborhood has a pool and is in an extremely convenient part of town. Still feels new and just needs you!
